title: EastEnders: Secrets from the Square
overview: EastEnders: Secrets from the Square is presented by Stacey Dooley who sits down each week in Ian Beale's restaurant, Walford East, with two different members of the cast to reflect on their time on the show, tease what's to come when EastEnders returns as well as the occasional sneak peek behind the scenes.Legends of Albert Square including Letitia Dean, Adam Woodyatt, Diane Parish, Tameka Empson, Danny Dyer and Kellie Bright to name just a few, will be looking back to their first memories of the show, the juiciest dramas to hit Walford and telling stories from behind-the-scene
